Class CandidateElementPosition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.crawljax.plugins.crawloverview.model.CandidateElementPosition

  • @Immutable
public class CandidateElementPosition
extends Object
    Position of a candidate element of a state. This type is used to build the overlays of screenshot to show where the CandidateElements were located.
